    {"who":"Eddy Florian","when":"06/24/2026 03:40 PM","label":"CLIENT ENGAGEMENT","body":"06/22/2026 — CSM check-in call completed. Dean was candid and acknowledged the team is working hard. Communication has improved noticeably since construction started. Frustrations centered on the pre-construction phase feeling inactive, design options sometimes feeling narrowed to move things along, and one inaccurate demo completion email. He is not pointing fingers, just wants to feel the goal is for him to be genuinely happy with the result. Nihaar asked to send a quick project update. CSM follow-up later this week."},
    {"who":"Sagar Patel","when":"06/22/2026 07:03 PM","label":"SITE MEETING","body":"Sagar and Nihaar met with Dean to discuss the lights, blinds, PTAC, windowsills and other minor work around the apartment. We are waiting on the client to send us the specs for lights and blinds. We are reaching out to PTAC vendors and stone installers while finishing minor work in the apartment. We would start framing now."},
    {"who":"Lorena Davila","when":"06/21/2026 03:31 PM","label":"INTERIOR DESIGN","body":"06/15 – 06/19: Completed the post-demo walkthrough on Tuesday the 16th. Verified the kitchen and bathroom dimensions on site."},
